+ Configure\nCheckpoint Locations
++ What is a Checkpoint?
+++_ Stores offset / progress info
+++_ Enables restart without reprocessing
+++_ Guarantees exactly-once semantics
++ Requirements
+++_ Each query needs unique checkpoint path
+++_ Sharing checkpoints causes errors
+++_ Store in durable location (ADLS)
-- Best Practices
---_ Use Azure Data Lake Storage
---_ Avoid lifecycle policies that delete files
---_ Keep small but treat as critical
-- Configuration
---_ checkpointLocation option in writeStream
---_ Set before starting any streaming query
---_ Verify on restart: resumes from last commit
@endmindmap
